headline: Trane Technologies to Present at the Citi Global Industrial Tech and Mobility Conference
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, February 06, 2026--Trane Technologies plc (NYSE: TT) a global climate innovator, today announced that company leadership will participate in a fireside chat at the Citi Global Industrial Tech Conference. They will speak at 10:30 a.m. ET on Wednesday, February 18, 2026.

headline: Trane Technologies and CIT Collaborate to Establish Centre for Sustainable Refrigeration and Climate Control in India
summary: Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT), a global leader in climate innovation, has taken a bold step toward accelerating sustainable climate solutions in India with the inauguration of the new Centre for Sustainable Refrigeration and Climate Control at Cambridge Institute of Technology (CIT), Bengaluru.
